Water-resistant high vis jacket in thermal softshell fabric with 4-way stretch. Four zipped front pockets. High collar with detachable hood. Ergonomic pre-shaped sleeves and adjustable cuffs. Reflectors on front, back and on sleeves for high visibility in the dark.

fields.name: Jacket Joshuan JH Collection® OLIVE GREEN
fields.description:
Waterproof, breathable jacket in tailored style. Two large zipped front pockets, one zipped inner pocket. Drawstring at back of waist for optimal fit. Brushed polyester jersey inside collar. Long zipped riding vent at back. Thumb holes at ends of sleeves. Waterproofed with Rudolf Bionic Finish Eco.
5000 mm water column.
5000 MVT breathability.
Two-way front zip.
Removable hood.
Wash 40°.

fields.name: Jacket Tone CRW® NAVY
fields.description:
Waterproof riding jacket designed for comfort and freedom of movement. Mesh lining for improved ventilation. Ergonomic pre-shaped sleeves with adjustable Velcro fastening at cuffs. Two zipped riding vents at back. Three zipped front pockets and zipped inner pocket. Treated with Rudolf Bionic Finish Eco.
5000 mm water column.
5000 MVT breathability.
Reflective details.
Taped seams.
Two-way front zip.
Removable hood.
Wash 40°.

fields.name: Jacket Tammy CRW® BRIGHT AQUA
fields.description:
Quilted, padded jacket with non-detachable hood. Two zipped front pockets. Waterproofed with Rudolf Bionic Finish Eco.

fields.name: Jacket Tammy CRW® BLACK

fields.name: Gloves Muenster Roeckl® GREY
fields.description:
Gloves with thin, elastic Vita Lycra on back of hand and ROECK-AIR on the inside for good fit and breathability. A hardwearing glove with slim fit and excellent grip. Touchscreen compatible.
Wash 30°.

fields.name: Gloves Milano Roeckl® NAVY
fields.description:
The Milano glove is made of high-quality materials and features ROECKL's exclusive COMFORT CUT, which ensures a comfortable fit without uncomfortable seams. The backhand is made of stretch Spandex, while the palm is made of digital suede. This material is flexible and durable. It provides a perfect grip of the reigns to give you good contact with your horse. Featuring a smart design where the palm material goes down round the wrist and up onto the backhand, where the material is held together with a practical fastener without uncomfortable seams.
Wash 30°.

fields.name: Gloves Blocka CRW® BLACK
fields.description:
Beautiful, soft riding gloves in synthetic suede, with a warm fleece lining. Reinforced palms.
Wash 30°.

fields.name: Gloves Grip Roeckl® NAVY
fields.description:
Durable, classic-style riding gloves. Made from light, flexible and breathable synthetic leather. Fits like a second skin, giving a real feel for the reins and excellent grip. Touch-screen compatible.
Wash 30°.

fields.name: Gloves Dea CRW® WHITE
fields.description:
Stylish cotton glove with PVC dots and velcro fastening.
Wash 40°.

fields.name: Gloves Margit CRW® DARK BROWN
fields.description: Gloves with soft waxed goatskin on palm and at wear points. Stretchy polyester on back of hand. Elastic around wrist for extra flexible fit.

fields.name: Gloves Ekemir CRW® BLACK
fields.description:

fields.description:

fields.name: Gloves Top Spin Winter CRW® NAVY

fields.description:
Riding helmet padded with microfibre suede. Size is adjustable to ensure a perfect fit. XS: 52-54. S: 54-56. M: 56-58. L: 59-61.
Weight approx. 450 g.
Soft peak for reduced risk of injury
Size adjustment.
Three-point fastening.
Front and back ventilation.
Ventilation through bobble.
Washable functional lining.
Wash 40°.

fields.name: Riding helmet VG1 Advantage CRW®
fields.description:
Elegant riding helmet with ABS outershell and metallic details with decorative middle section. Size can be adjusted with a screw at the back for a perfect fit. Adjustable nylon chin strap with PU leather. Removable and washable lining. S: 53-55, M: 56-58, L: 59-61.
Weight approx. 420 g.
Size adjustment.
Three-point fastening.
Front and back ventilation.
Washable functional lining.

fields.name: Riding helmet VG1 Advantage Sun CRW® BLACK/GOLD
fields.description:
Lightweight riding helmet in matt ABS plastic with metallic detailing. With wide peak that provides protection from sunlight and bright spotlights. Ventilation slots at back and front help you stay cool when riding. Nylon harness with PU leather detailing and screw for adjusting the fit. Removable, washable lining helps keep the helmet fresh and clean. Size S: 53-55, M: 56-58, L: 59-61.
Size adjustment.
Three-point fastening.
Front and back ventilation.

fields.name: Riding helmet VG1 Advantage Sun CRW® NAVY
fields.description:
Lightweight riding helmet in matt ABS plastic with metallic detailing. With wide peak that provides protection from sunlight and bright spotlights. Ventilation slots at back and front help you stay cool when riding. Nylon harness with PU leather detailing and screw for adjusting the fit. Removable, washable lining helps keep the helmet fresh and clean. Size S: 53-55, M: 56-58, L: 59-61.
Size adjustment.
Three-point fastening.
Front and back ventilation.

fields.name: Riding helmet VG1 AYR8 Plus Charles Owen BLACK/GOLD
fields.description:
Leather-look riding helmet with a low profile. Soft leather-look GRpx chin strap. Twelve discreet front and rear ventilation slots help maintain a comfortable temperature when riding. Removable and washable lining. Available in six colours and in sizes 52-60. For more information contact our customer services.
Size adjustment.
Front and back ventilation.
Washable functional lining.

fields.name: Riding helmet VG1 Matrix Mips JH Collection® NAVY
fields.description:
Riding helmet with MIPS, a technology that mimics the brain's natural safety system. When the head is subjected to angled impact, this system allows the brain to move in the cerebrospinal fluid, which reduces trauma to the brain. The MIPS system has an integrated low-friction liner that can absorb part of the energy that could otherwise cause brain damage in the event of angled impact. Removable and washable lining. Adjustable with one button at back. S: 52-54 cm. M: 55-57 cm. L: 58-60 cm. PU chin strap.
MIPS* Safety system.
Size adjustment.
Three-point fastening.
Front and back ventilation.

fields.name: Riding helmet VG1 EQ3 Lynx Smooth Top Mips Back on Track® BLACK
fields.description:
Riding helmet with MIPS, a technology that mimics the brain's natural safety system. When the head is subjected to angled impact, this system allows the brain to move in the cerebrospinal fluid, which reduces trauma to the brain. The helmet is equipped with an MIPS system, an integrated low-friction liner that can absorb part of the energy that could otherwise cause brain damage. The helmet is designed and approved for use in all riding disciplines. Adjustable with one button at back. Weight 600 g. S: 50-53 cm. M: 54-58 cm. L: 59-61 cm.
MIPS* Safety system.
Soft peak for reduced risk of injury
Three-point fastening.
Front and back ventilation.
Ear protection bars.
Washable functional lining.

fields.name: Riding helmet VG1 Crystalline CRW® NAVY
fields.description:
Riding helmet in microfibre decorated with crystals and glitter. Adjustable size. Nylon chin strap. Removable and washable lining. XS: 49-51 cm. S: 52-54 cm. M: 55-57 cm. L: 58-60 cm.
Size adjustment.
Three-point fastening.

fields.name: Riding helmet VG1 YR8 Sparkling Charles Owen NAVY
fields.description:
Riding helmet in microfibre with decorative glitter panel at centre. Four discreet ventilation slots help maintain a comfortable temperature when riding. Nylon harness and chin strap. Certified according to PAS 015:2011.
Three-point fastening.

fields.name: Riding helmet VG1 Artemis LAMI-CELL BLACK
fields.description:
Riding helmet with glittery microsuede surface. With screw at back to adjust the fit. Wide peak provides protection from sunlight and bright spotlights. Removable and washable lining.
Size adjustment.

fields.name: Riding helmet VG1 Pardus Smooth Top Back on Track® BLACK
fields.description: EQ3 Pardus with screw adjustment system for optimal fit. With a smooth, matt outer finish. Pardus has good ventilation thanks to several different air holes on the front and back of the helmet. The lining in the helmet is removable and made of Coolmax which transports away moisture. The lining can easily be washed clean with lukewarm water. Pardus is equipped with the same MIPS rotation system. The MIPS Brain Protection System significantly increases protection against brain damage. The MIPS system mimics the natural safety system in the human head. When the head is subjected to angled impact, this system allows the brain to move in the cerebrospinal fluid, which reduces trauma to the brain in the event of angled impact. The MIPS system is the yellow moving shell you can see inside all Back on Track helmets. The helmet has a fit for slightly more elongated heads and you may need to go up one size from your previous helmet.

fields.name: Combined noseband bridle Winford Fairfield® DARK BROWN
fields.description:
Combined noseband bridle with light-coloured decorative stitching on noseband and headband. Soft lining at noseband, neck and browband. Anatomically shaped headpiece. Fully removable Aachen strap. Cheek pieces with bit rings.
Silver coloured buckle.
Without reins.

fields.name: Bridles Ashton Fairfield® DARK BROWN
fields.description:
Bridle with wide crown piece and soft padding, designed to reduce pressure on the horse's neck. Quick-release fastener under the jaw with a moveable panel, adjustable height and length. Extra padding on bridge of nose. Curved browband with soft lining.
Silver coloured buckle.
Without reins.

fields.name: Drop noseband bridle Falston Fairfield® DARK BROWN
fields.description:

Silver coloured buckle.
Without reins.

fields.name: Sidepull Fairfield® BLACK
fields.description:
Sidepull bridle with soft lining at noseband, neck and browband.
Silver coloured buckle.
Without reins.

fields.name: Grackle bridle Harlow Fairfield® BLACK
fields.description:
Grackle bridle with pre-shaped nose piece and soft panel under jaw. Wide shaped neck piece, curved browband. Soft padding on neck, browband and nose. White decorative seams.
Silver coloured buckle.
Reins not included.

fields.name: Combined noseband bridle Heart Fairfield® DARK BROWN
fields.description:
Combined noseband bridle with soft lining at noseband and browband. Decorated with silver-coloured heart with white rhinestones.
Silver coloured buckle.
Without reins.

fields.name: Bridles Croston Fairfield® DARK BROWN
fields.description:
Bridle with curved, soft padded noseband designed to prevent pressure over sensitive areas. Anatomically shaped crownpiece with a cut-out section in the middle. The bit is attached to an adjustable leather strap. Curved lined browband. Without throat lash.
Silver coloured buckle.
Without reins.

fields.name: Bridles Croston Fairfield® BLACK
fields.description:
Bridle with curved, soft padded noseband designed to prevent pressure over sensitive areas. Anatomically shaped crownpiece with a cut-out section in the middle. The bit is attached to an adjustable leather strap. Curved lined browband. Without throat lash.
Silver coloured buckle.
Without reins.

fields.name: Combined noseband bridle Axford Fairfield® DARK BROWN
fields.description:
Combined noseband bridle decorated with brass-coloured clinchers on headband and noseband, which have soft lining.
Without reins.

fields.name: Bridles Catani JH Collection® BLACK
fields.description:
Combined noseband bridle made from European leather. Slightly curved 3.5 cm wide noseband with soft padding. Removable pullback quick-release fastener. Fully removable Aachen strap and throat lash. Curved lined browband. Wide neck with padding in two sections. Cheek pieces with bit rings.
Silver coloured buckle.
Without reins.

fields.name: Combined noseband bridle Modin JH Collection® COGNAC
fields.description:
Combined noseband bridle made of Swedish vegetable-tanned leather from Tärnsjö Tannery (not lined). Soft lining at noseband and neck. Removable Aachen strap.
Silver coloured buckle.

fields.name: Combined noseband bridle Chelsea Fairfield® BLACK
fields.description:
Combined noseband bridle. Round-sewn, with 4 cm wide, lacquered noseband and curved browband. Crown piece with soft lining and raised edges allowing the strap for the noseband and cheek pieces to pass above it. Pull-back fastening.
Silver coloured buckle.
Without reins.

fields.name: Body protector Junior Minerva CRW® BLACK
fields.description: The cushion-like panels in the vest provide maximum protection from knocks and impact on one side and a perfect fit on the other side. The panels are positioned to provide maximum freedom of movement with the highest possible protection. Easily adjustable at sides and over shoulders for an optimal fit. The material, fit and function combined with the highest safety standards on the market, EN 13158 and Level 3, BETA certified, provide a vest that is ideal for both beginners and more advanced riders.

fields.name: Body protector Men’s Outlyne Airowear BLACK
fields.description:
Velcro on waist and shoulders, easily adjustable. Front zip. Ventilated, soft stuffing.M3 (size 46) M4 (size 48) M5 (size 50).
Removable outer.
CE and BETA 2009 level 3 Approved
Hand wash.

fields.name: Body protector Adult Ares CRW® NAVY
fields.description:
Separate panels for ultimate comfort and movement. Adjustable with Velcro on shoulders and lacing down the sides. A good value for money and popular body protector. Front zip CE, Level 3 approved.
Hand wash.

fields.name: Back Protector Ballistic Flex Fit Komperdell PINK
fields.description:
Lightweight back protector with Austrian design with ergonomic fit. Slim fit and great comfort with soft and flexible foam system. When the back protector is warmed up by the wearer's body heat, it conforms to the body. Suited for use under your jacket because of its light and smooth design. It has high breathability, helping to maintain a constant comfortable body temperature during exercise. Protects the back during training and recreational riding. The back protector has protective plates on the front and sides, which are adjusted automatically when the zip is done up. EN 1621-2 (motorcycle standard).
CE Approved.
Wash 30°.

fields.name: D-ring bit Novocontact Sprenger SENSOGAN
fields.description: 2-piece bit shaped to increase area of contact with tongue without pressing against palate. When the rider pulls the reins, the bit is angled forwards which narrows the point of contact. This improves communication between horse and rider. When the reins are released, the bit returns to its default position with the broad part resting softly and comfortably against the horse's tongue. Ring 65 mm. Made of Sensogan.

fields.name: Bit KK Ultra 2-Type Sprenger SENSOGAN
fields.description: 3-piece bit that combines the benefits of loose and fixed rings. Sits well in the mouth due to a slightly shorter central part that is angled 45 degrees forward. Suitable for horses with sensitive mouth corners and horses that can be difficult to turn. Ring 70 mm. Made of Sensogan.

fields.name: Egg bit Three sectioned Sprenger SILVER
fields.description: 3-piece bit. Ring 65 cm.

fields.name: Bridle bit Soft Beris
fields.description: A soft, straight bridal bit with a slightly thinner mouth section. Ring 7.5 cm Ø. Handmade in Germany. Made of plastic approved for food contact. The bit should be attached so that the engraved bit ring is on the left side of the horse's mouth.

fields.name: Kimblewick bit Extra Soft Beris
fields.description: Extra-soft Kimblewick bit from Beris of Germany with a thinner section in the middle. Handmade in Germany. Made of plastic approved for food contact. The bit should be attached so that the engraved bit ring is on the left side of the horse's mouth.

fields.name: Pelham bit Comfort Thin short shanks Beris
fields.description: The Comfort Thin mouthpiece has the same design as the Comfort Bar but is 15 mm thinner. Recommended for horses with small mouths and for ponies. A pelham bit is a classic bit that can be used for hot and strong horses. It applies pressure on the neck and lower jaw. This bit can be used with a delta or with double reins. The bit's effect can be modified by using it with or without a chain.

fields.name: Bridle bit Comfort thin Bar Beris
fields.description: Comfort is an anatomical bit with a 6 cm ring. It rests equally on the tongue and bars and is shaped to allow more room and mobility for the tongue. Thanks to its shape, the Comfort Bar lies very still in the horse's mouth, and is suitable for young or sensitive horses. Loose Ring has a loose ring running through a copper sleeve, which increases its lifespan._x000D_ _x000D_

fields.name: Bit Loose ring snaffle Nathe SILVER
fields.description: Sensogan middle piece encourages acceptance of the bit and stimulates saliva production. The bit provides direct and precise action and distributes pressure evenly on the tongue and lower jaw. Suitable for all disciplines and levels. The bit ring protects the corners of the mouth.

fields.name: Bit Nathe SILVER
fields.description: A mouth and tongue friendly bit with a classic design. Joints made of hypoallergenic plastic. Distributes pressure evenly. Suitable for all disciplines and levels.

fields.name: Bit Standard snaffle Nathe SILVER
fields.description: Flexible mouthpiece with low port. The bit ring is designed to give clearer signals when turning. The bit lies firmly in the mouth and is suitable for horses that lose contact with the bit. Bit ring protects corners of mouth. Steel in centre.

fields.name: Bit Mullen Mouth Nathe SILVER
fields.description: Mouthpiece with port. The bit ring is designed to give clearer signals when turning. The bit lies firmly in the mouth and is suitable for horses that lose contact with the bit. Bit ring protects corners of mouth. Steel in centre.

fields.name: Bit Metalab SILVER
fields.description: A straight bit with a Mullen barrel mouthpiece. This bit provides good contact with the horse, and the moveable centre section can also help if your horse tends to put its tongue over the bit.

fields.name: Bit Baucher Metalab SILVER

fields.name: Jumping saddle Amo Pessoa® BLACK
fields.description: Close contact jumping saddle. This saddle has been specially designed for the Swedish market in collaboration with Pessoa's saddle makers and some of Sweden's leading saddle testers. Rodrigo Amo is based on earlier Pessoa saddles but has a wider channel, a softer seat and wider and slightly longer panels, allowing greater freedom over the withers. Rodrigo Amo has a narrow waist and a deeper seat, giving the rider closer contact with the horse. Pre-oiled quality leather for a good grip. The saddle comes with two different knee blocks.

fields.name: Jumping saddle Fazzino Lippo BLACK
fields.description: French-inspired jumping saddle with more forward cut flap and deep seat. Soft AMS upholstery. Replaceable gullet plate (330401). Suitable for horses with normal to straight back. Supplied with gullet plate size: MW.

fields.name: Dressage saddle Vanessa Lippo BLACK
fields.description: Dressage saddle in double-stitched leather. Slightly narrower middle, making it easier for the rider to reach the correct position. Soft AMS upholstery. Replaceable gullet plate, item no. 330401. Supplied with gullet plate size MW.

fields.name: Jumping saddle Gen-X Elite Pony Pessoa® BLACK
fields.description: Jumping saddle with narrow waist suitable for smaller riders. Fits ponies with a broad and straight back. Now with larger skirts and a deeper seat. Made of English oiled leather with excellent grip. AMS® panel. Moveable front and rear thigh blocks. Replaceable gullet plates (330401). Supplied with gullet plate in size Medium-Wide.

fields.name: Jumping saddle Gen-X Elite Pony Pessoa® DARK BROWN

fields.name: Disinfectant Spray EKODES Pet Showmaster®
fields.description: EKODES™ Petspray is a safe, effective alternative to conventional pet care products, completely free from toxic chemicals. The active ingredient is hypochlorous acid, a completely natural substance. Natural – It is naturally present in the white blood cells in the immune system of humans and animals, where it effectively fights invasion from bacteria and other pathogens. Safe – It causes no harm to humans or animals, whether it comes into contact with the skin, eyes or nose or is inhaled or ingested. 100% environmentally friendly. Effective – It eliminates 99.999% of bacteria, fungi and viruses in just seconds. During use, keep excess hair away from the wound site and cut hair if necessary. Apply generously. The spray cleanses, disinfects and promotes healing.
